```typescript
<Image
  src="/images/hero.png"
  alt="Hero image"
  width={1200}
  height={800}
  priority // For above-the-fold images
/>
```

3. **Respect Reduced Motion:**

```typescript
const prefersReducedMotion = useReducedMotion();
const animationDuration = prefersReducedMotion ? 0 : 0.5;
```

